casebody.data:
Russell B. SEYMOUR, etc., et al. v. WESTERN FRUIT GROWERS, Inc. No. 8551. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 24, 1937. G. V. Weikert, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and MATHEWS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of appellee, ordered appeal herein dismissed for failure of appellants to file record and docket cause; that a decree of dismissal be filed and entered accordingly; mandate forthwith.
